v 3
d 'raincloud': Raincloud plots combining density, scatter, and box elements
d
d Produces raincloud plots (Allen et al. 2019) that combine a
d half-violin kernel density (cloud), jittered raw data points
d (rain), and box-and-whisker summary into a single figure.
d Supports group stratification, horizontal/vertical orientation,
d and extensive customization of all elements.
d
d Requires: Stata version 16+
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260314
d License: MIT
d
d Author: Timothy P Copeland
d Department of Clinical Neuroscience
d Karolinska Institutet
d
d KW: raincloud plot
d KW: visualization
d KW: distribution
d KW: kernel density
d KW: violin plot
d KW: jitter
d KW: box plot
d
f raincloud.ado
f raincloud.sthlp
